---
title: Carb Smart Plant-Based Protein and Sweet Potato Salad with Beyond Meat®
description: A generous drizzle of creamy and herby sun-dried tomato dressing is the star of this recipe. Smoky Smart Beyond Meat®  is cooked and tossed with roasted sweet potatoes, tangy marinated radishes and a salad topper for a meal that only skimps on carbs, not flavour.
